    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable, java.util.Collection, java.util.List, java.util.RandomAccess, org.json.simple.JSONAware, org.json.simple.JSONStreamAware

    public class ShrgJSONArray
extends org.json.simple.JSONArray
    Each element of the array is a JSONObject having an only "key : value" pair. Furthermore The class extends its parent by adding the direct access capability with the clone(JSONArray) method.
